{"tid":1717801,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"圍爐取暖","createTime":"2019-11-13T16:43:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-15T07:22:14.000Z","uid":314733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"2517450fb37ba4cd510118e9119aa449f4273f37","tid":1717801,"uid":314733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T16:43:33.000Z","msg":"無論前線或者和理非都好 <br />\n大家都會有攰嘅時候<br />\n有人要面對住家人嘅反對<br />\n有人要面對住生活上嘅壓力<br />\n有人要面對住有機會被捕嘅壓力<br />\n太多啦 我唔諗住打晒出嚟<br />\n<br />\n希望你地都可以調整到嗰情緒先去做下一步嘅嘢<br />\n有時都要俾自己抖氣嘅空間<br />\n唔想抖嘅唔緊要 不過記住有咩事都要同身邊最信得過嘅人講 唔好收埋俾自己一個面對<br />\n<br />\n如果冇就可以喺度講 一齊分享同分擔<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n手足們要頂住 <br />\n加油 反抗 報仇"},{"pid":"d3ba0a7f0df5f6aa01d14e894ce285c225e58b9e","tid":1717801,"uid":314733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T16:44:11.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"df2d9c73f3653a2a4c5d39035d2a72b16dfa2e0f","tid":1717801,"uid":314733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T16:44:23.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3217570acfebee2f2e293232297fde55d525f397","tid":1717801,"uid":275719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T17:34:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90fd641d6d1441be48c46e246b4fb000adf5d92b","tid":1717801,"uid":314733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3217570acfebee2f2e293232297fde55d525f397","tid":1717801,"uid":275719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T17:34:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T18:34:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"500fb610488932e98a498e953d92fa676d482a57","tid":1717801,"uid":275719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"90fd641d6d1441be48c46e246b4fb000adf5d92b","tid":1717801,"uid":314733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3217570acfebee2f2e293232297fde55d525f397","tid":1717801,"u